casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Kasson.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Kasson (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 1203.]

(Nos. 91-1914 and 91-1742 Submitted October 9, 1991 Decided October 10, 1991.)

The resignation of Lee B. Kasson, Jr. as an attorney, Registration No. 0002133, is accepted. Sua sponte, 91-1742, Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Kasson, Disciplinary Docket No. 90-41, is dismissed as moot.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
